		<td rowspan=2 bgcolor="#050A0E" width=1><img src="/i/p.gif" height=1 width=1 border=0 alt=""><br></td>
	
		<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; 
		" 
			>
			<DIV>This thread is not a complaint. It's a request. It's really one I've had in mind for a long time, but with the advent of the progression servers it seems much more of a possibility now. </DIV>
<DIV><BR>It appears to me that most of the whining is coming from people who seem to be *opposing* the request. Perhaps it somehow threatens them, but I can't imagine how unless they are plat resellers or something. </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Ah but if I were to dream, I would make a PVP progression server (with the cheating hacks eliminated) and a 15 hour per week time limit... and I think I'd probably make everything no drop AND only lootable by those in the group that killed a mob - and have a fairly tight group level difference requirement. Then again, I'd never create POK or the Bazaar either. </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>I don't mind if you don't share my dream, you can continue doing exactly what you are now, I won't complain <img src='/i/smilies/16x16_smiley-wink.gif' width=16 height=16 border=0> </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>/wave</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>	
		</td></tr>
