		<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; 
		" 
			>
			<DIV></DIV>
<DIV>Most people knew this would happen.The people that joined the progression server and thought they were gonna be on the same level as the ubers they envy so much are getting a rude awakening.Now they want yet another server.Wake up people.If you are a casual player or non raider you will always be behind.No matter what kind of server you try and dream up.Making a server with restricted play time is the most selfish idea that I have ever heard.I thought it was all about "reliving the old times and enjoying old eq".When in fact,just like many people stated,you could have done that on a normal server.The reason you didn't ,is because for alot of you it was never about that.It was about finally being on a server where you didnt have to look at the ubers and all of the space they had put between themselves and you.Now look at you.The expansions will keep being unlocked at a furious pace.The only thing making this server accomplished was giving hardcore players with maxed out aa's a place to dominate in thier non raiding hours.Maybe they can make a server where no one can get passed level 1 and can't wear any gear.Then MAYBE you would be happy and drop the jealousy you have towards peoples that play more than you and are just better players than you in general.</DIV>	
		</td></tr>
